{"tid":1177522,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"『冇圖』侵侵個女泳裝大解放","createTime":"2019-05-29T21:04:23.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-29T23:11:24.000Z","uid":130105,"like":1,"dislike":13,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"d2f67c42caefeac8c131b5c2a11295150710ac56","tid":1177522,"uid":130105,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-29T21:04:23.000Z","msg":"嘩，縮陽<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n&bull;Tiffany, 25, and her boyfriend Michael, 25, have spent the past few weeks together enjoying a getaway in Europe, traveling to London, then Cannes for the Film Festival, then a trip back to London before Monaco<br />\n&bull;The couple were seen relaxing on a yacht, where they are believed to be staying, on Wednesday, alongside Tiffany's close pal Peter, who is the son of model and actress Stephanie Seymour   <br />\n&bull;First daughter Tiffany wore a pale blue $158 swimsuit from Everything But Water, and added a lacy white cover-up to complete her look, as well as a pair of round $620 Gucci sunglasses <br />\n&bull;The blonde, who is on summer break from Georgetown Law, also went barefoot, and at one point was seen lying down on a sofa while her boyfriend Michael tenderly rubbed her arm   <br />\n&bull;She and her friends are currently staying on a 236.2 ft charter superyacht that boasts 15 rooms with space for a whopping 30 guests and 31 crew members and costs $618,000 per week to rent <br />\n&bull;The vessel, which was built by Astral Yachts, is worth an estimated $59,030,000 <br />\n&bull;Tiffany is thought to be returning to London at the start of next week in order to join her father, President Trump, for his state visit to the British capital, alongside her half siblings, Ivanka, Donald Jr, and Eric <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.dailymail.co.uk/1s/2019/05/29/19/14112666-7083615-image-m-130_1559153313023.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.dailymail.co.uk%2F1s%2F2019%2F05%